### Search product categories - by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/search?name=electron

### Search product categories - by name, active only (default)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/search?name=gaming

### Search product categories - by name, including inactive
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/search?name=gaming&active=false

### Search product categories - no results
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/search?name=nonexistent